Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: fastDummies, janitor
Enhances: rkward
Description: An RKWard plugin to create dummy variables (one-hot
        encoding) from survey or dataframe objects using the
        'fastDummies' package. Features integrated label preservation
        and janitor cleaning.
